@node REGLES "The rules of the game"
   If you know the rules of BomberMan, you know the rules of Bomber Gug.
   For the people who don't know BomberMan, in the game, the last player who is on
   the screen is the winner.For that, the player must kill the other to win.To kill
   the other players, you have to put bombs.And after a few second, the bomb explode
   and fire appear on the 4 directions : up, down, right, left.If a player is on fire,
   he die.On the screen, there are bricks,if the fire appear on a brick,the brick
   explode and a bonus (or a malus) can appear.The bonus are (you have to find yourself
   how they are in the game)
    - More fire : Fire of the bombs are more long
    - More bomb  : You can put +1 bomb.
    - ?              : Random bonus
    - Mega fire   : Fire of the the bombs are very very long for few seconds
    - Fire wall : fire go trough of the wall but no bonus appear.
    - Automatic bomb : when you go forward , a bomb appear automaticelly.Dangerous !!
    - 1 bomb : the other player had 1 bomb
    - Boum : explode all the bombs on the screen.It can be very dangerous !

   Keys : click @{"here" LINK TOUCHES}
@endnode
