@node TOUCHES "What are the keys of the game ?"
     Esc .................. in the presentation : quit the game.
                            in the game : a @{"menu" LINK ESC} apear.
     Joystick :
     Up ................. The player goes up.
     Down ............... The player goes down.
     Right .............. The player goes right.
     Left ............... The player goes left.
     Fire ............... The player puts a bomb.
@endnode
